comments.content:
I think this is an old typeface called Profil. I’m pretty sure we have found digital versions of this.

- Mike Yanega

Bitstream sells it as [Decorated 035](http://web.archive.org/web/20080825150017/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/bitstream/decorated-035/).

- Mike Yanega
